    "Considering how recommender systems are designed and implemented offers further evidence of why they're prone to allocating attention in morally problematic ways.",
    "Since these tools are meant to dynamically model and predict users' preferences based on their behavior, reinforcement learning (RL) is an especially powerful technique for training them.",
    "10 Another common application of RL, which helpfully illustrates how it works, is game playing.",
    "RL can teach an AI system to play a game by specifying the object of the game in a reward function which reinforces goalapproximating behavior.",
    "With a well-specified reward function and enough opportunities to refine its approach through interaction with its environment, an AI system can learn to play a wide range of games, often at superhuman levels."
